    strengths: "Waters live with conviction, are bold and courageous. 
    Healthy Waters are willing to take a stand and sacrifice themselves for what‚Äôs right, and keep the mission moving forward; they are sensible, responsible, ethical, self- disciplined, just, fair, tolerant of failure‚Äîboth theirs and others‚Äîand accepting of their limits and losses.",
    weaknesses: "For Waters, the besetting struggle is anger. 
    The underlying emotion Waters are trying to conquer is guilt. Waters often carry a suppressed anger because nothing is ever good enough‚Äî including and especially themselves. This anger is driven by an exaggerated sense of guilt and a feeling of not measuring up, which leads Waters to be very hard on themselves. Few casual observers would suspect how much Waters are suffering from the attacks of their Inner Critic. This is not only how Waters tend to relate to themselves, but to others, through performance and criticism."
)

